                    </div>
                    <span>I bought this book after reading a complimentary review online. Unfortunately, this book proved to be a very bland, unentertaining read about an unintelligent, vanilla main character who doesn't even give himself a chance to keep the money that he found.<P>Nothing spectacular really happens in the book; in fact, this probably would have been a better feature article for a second-tier major newspaper.<P> I found the characters very difficult to follow, much less get interested in. I do not recommend this book at all.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">not really that great</div>
